# === Lume Capital — deploy allowlist ===
# Only the built page (index.html) and the assets it references are tracked/pushed.
# All brand-source files (EPS/JPG/PDF/extra PNGs), content drafts, compliance docs,
# working files, and build notes stay local and are never pushed.

# 1) Ignore everything by default
/*

# 2) Repo essentials
!.gitignore
!index.html
# design-token reference for the full TailPress/Tailwind build
!lume-design-system.css

# 3) Root-level assets referenced by index.html
!nwm-logo-horizontal-white.svg
!CFP-logo.jpeg
!MDRT-logo.jpeg
!chris-moore-pic.jpg
!lume-lifestyle.jpg
!james-taylor-pic.jpg
!vanessa-pic.jpg
!zach-pic.jpg
!connor-pic.jpg
!sydney-pic.jpg
!kevin-pic.jpg

# 4) Keep only the one PNG referenced (inside PNG/)
!PNG/
PNG/*
!PNG/2_LumeCapital_FullColor_Reverse_Horizontal.png
